twisted brambles and other plants seems to grow over and cover the city,
blocking out the sunlight.  It's obviously ideal living conditions for the
trolls, who abhor sunlight.  You are checked over by a guard, and he
grudgingly allows you into the city.  Seems like they don't take too kindly
to outsiders.  The sprawling city lies to the north.  
